                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>If the pale stranger's murderer dies, the pale stranger is immediately destroyed. A pale stranger that can't sense their murderer must attempt a @Check[type:flat|dc:11] once every 24 hours to avoid becoming @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Immobilized] and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone]; they immediately rise again once they can sense their murderer. A murderer who becomes undead does not trigger the pale stranger's destruction until the murderer is finally destroyed. The pale stranger gains a +2 status bonus to checks and DCs against their murderer.</p>"
